description:
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hampshire County Council has excellent opportunities available for &lt;strong&gt;care assistants&lt;/strong&gt;to join our new provider service we are setting up in &lt;strong&gt;Gosport.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hampshire County Councils’ Adults Health and Care provide a range of residential care and nursing services for older people across the county, some of whom are living with dementia. &lt;strong&gt;Clarence Unit&lt;/strong&gt; is opening to support adults with complex health needs following their discharge from hospital. To find out more about this unique unit please click here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Life experience is often more importantthan work experience in these roles. Our main priority is to find people who share our values of being person centred, working together, accountability and resilience – the rest we can teach you, could this be you?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;No two days are the same in this varied and rewarding role.As a general guide, your duties may include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;• Supporting individuals with personal care&lt;br /&gt;• Support with hydration and nutrition&lt;br /&gt;• Moving and positioning&lt;br /&gt;• Accurate record keeping&lt;br /&gt;• Undertaking activities such as entertainment and recreation to enhance the wellbeing of individuals&lt;br /&gt;• Supporting Individuals with medication&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Excellent benefits include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;• Flexible working&lt;br /&gt;• Comprehensive training&lt;br /&gt;• Staff Uniform&lt;br /&gt;• Contributory pension scheme &lt;br /&gt;• HCC funded DBS checks and updates&lt;br /&gt;• Staff Wellbeing Service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hampshire cares, could you?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
